    // {"name":"电影慰时光 | 华语怀旧文艺片精选","id":490158454,"trackNumberUpdateTime":1662764135495,"status":0,"userId":311877725,"createTime":1476923681679,"updateTime":1663125659000,"subscribedCount":57802,"trackCount":90,"cloudTrackCount":0,"coverImgUrl":"http://p2.music.126.net/Dn8SeEUr-7--FlrZ-LKVAw==/18601537720555575.jpg","coverImgId":18601537720555576,"description":"封面： 花樣年華 (2000)\n华语电影百年，声光交织历史，那些从经典银幕里流淌出的乐曲，因与电影自然贴切和意境一致而相得益彰，更经岁月沉淀而愈发醇厚，成为我们难以忘记的声光记忆。光影流年，岁月留声……\n\n在这个世界上秋天深了\n该得到的尚未得到\n该丧失的早已丧失\n——海子《秋》\n\n秋天是个略显伤感\n适合怀念的季节\n总会想起过往岁月里\n一些人 一些事 一些歌和一些电影\n以电影慰时光\n念想在落叶纷飞的深秋\n\n原声配乐专辑名或后缀就是所属电影。\n仅列出没有标识的\n\n1.城南旧事\n7.阳光灿烂的日子\n11.滚滚红尘\n35.南国再见，南国\n37.最好的时光\n38-40.牯岭街少年S人S件\n41.恐Bu分子\n42.一一\n45.洞\n46.天桥不见了\n47.青少年哪吒\n53.笼民\n60.甜言蜜语\n\n编排按电影时代或一定关系承启，建议第一次听时按顺序播放\n\n2016.10.20创建，2022.9.8再次更新","tags":["影视原声","经典","怀旧"],"playCount":5361565,"trackUpdateTime":1663828549389,"specialType":0,"totalDuration":0,"creator":{"defaultAvatar":false,"province":530000,"authStatus":0,"followed":false,"avatarUrl":"http://p1.music.126.net/F7rbsWu7Io6xz1kQFhvoAQ==/109951166051235223.jpg","accountStatus":0,"gender":1,"city":532600,"birthday":310492800000,"userId":311877725,"userType":200,"nickname":"蝶影丛虫","signature":"默默向上游","description":"","detailDescription":"","avatarImgId":109951166051235220,"backgroundImgId":109951167626287980,"backgroundUrl":"http://p1.music.126.net/q4KtqSamM6skPurBgt8igQ==/109951167626287991.jpg","authority":0,"mutual":false,"expertTags":["影视原声","华语","欧美"],"experts":null,"djStatus":0,"vipType":11,"remarkName":null,"authenticationTypes":524352,"avatarDetail":{"userType":200,"identityLevel":4,"identityIconUrl":"https://p5.music.126.net/obj/wo3DlcOGw6DClTvDisK1/4761340194/0903/b735/7c7a/0dddcdf78047d397d24125840e54ab5b.png"},"anchor":false,"avatarImgIdStr":"109951166051235223","backgroundImgIdStr":"109951167626287991","avatarImgId_str":"109951166051235223"},"tracks":null,"subscribers":[{"defaultAvatar":false,"province":450000,"authStatus":0,"followed":false,"avatarUrl